    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> 9th level, Wrist-Mounted Grappling Hook</em></p>\n<p>After hitting a creature with your grappling hook, you can use the connection to deliver an at-will tech power. As a bonus action, you can cast an at-will tech power at the target with a range of touch. If the power requires an attack roll, you have advantage. If the target requires a saving throw, the target has disadvantage. </p>\n<p>Once you've used this feature, you can't use it again until you recover the hook.</p>",
